#: luci-app-mlo/htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/mlo.js:369
msgid ""
"A dedicated editor for OpenWrt Multi-Link Operation. Compared with the stock "
"Wireless page, this view can manage multi-radio <code>device</code> lists, "
"show MLD runtime state, and prefill safer MLO defaults."
msgstr ""
"这是一个专用于 OpenWrt 多链路操作（MLO）的编辑器。相比默认无线页面，它可以管"
"理多 radio 的 <code>device</code> 列表、显示 MLD 运行状态，并预填更安全的 "
"MLO 默认值。"

#: luci-app-mlo/htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/mlo.js:278
msgid "AP MLO is usually paired with WPA3-SAE or OWE"
msgstr "AP MLO 通常搭配 WPA3-SAE 或 OWE 使用"

